夏奇拉 (Shakira) 与 Fuerza Regida 全新合作《El Jefe》：立即串流https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/shakira-fuerza-regida-el-jefe-new-song-release-1235416436/  Thu, 21 Sep 2023 00:44:38 +0000 LatinMusicBBLatin https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235416436 The track marks the first collaborative effort between the two. <!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "><br><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/shakira/" target="_blank">夏奇拉</a>凭借这位哥伦比亚巨星与<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/fuerza-regida/" target="_blank">Fuerza Regida</a>合作的《El Jefe》踏入了新领域，该片已于周三（9 月 20 日）上映。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "><br>这位排行榜冠军艺术家上周首次调侃了这次合作，当时她分享了一段<a rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=87443X1644751&amp;isjs=1&amp;jv=15.4.2-stackpath&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Flatin%2Fshakira-fuerza-regida-el-jefe-new-song-release-1235416436%2F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxOvQWiMFId%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igshid%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D&amp;xs=1&amp;xtz=300&amp;xuuid=489d4d9dc212d52bf087e94ec92ea77d&amp;cci=9b9b80a218828900b98ff70f1baf6653" target="_blank">接受<em>《ET》</em>采访</a>的短片，其中她说：“我不是这首歌的老板，但请拭目以待。”然后，她分享了《El Jefe（老板）》的一个片段，这是关于一个拥有百万富翁心态但实际上没有钱的人的故事。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "><br>尽管夏奇拉之前的歌曲都包含了墨西哥地方音乐的元素，例如“Ciega, Sordomuda”中的墨西哥流浪乐队小号和带有乡村色彩的“Te Espero Sentada”，但这是她第一首成熟的墨西哥音乐歌曲。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "><br>在朗朗上口的走廊里，夏奇拉和 Fuerza 的主唱 JOP 唱出了对朝九晚五的工作的厌倦，尤其是他们傲慢的老板，以及辞职并成为自己老板的愿望。该音乐视频由全球巨星和地区城市表演者共同表演这首歌曲。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey"><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary"></h3><p>有关的</p></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><p><a tabindex="0" href="https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/shakira-latin-music-week-2023-panel-announced-1235386925/" class="lrv-u-flex lrv-a-unstyle-link lrv-u-color-brand-primary:hover"></a></p><div class="o-card__image-wrap lrv-u-flex-shrink-0 u-flex-basis-144 u-flex-basis-96@mobile-max"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><p><img class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/shakira-billboard-latin-music-week-2023-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&amp;h=147&amp;crop=1" alt="夏奇拉" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></p></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"></h3><p>夏奇拉将在迈阿密公告牌 2023 年拉丁音乐周上发表演讲</p></div><p><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"><br> 2023年9月20日<br></time></p></div><p></p></div></div><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "><br>夏奇拉与 Fuerza Regida 的合作反映了墨西哥音乐对当今拉丁音乐的主导地位和影响。随着像 Fuerza 这样的乐队走在前列，这一流派今年创下了纪录，在美国及其他地区越来越受欢迎。今年 5 月， <em>Billboard</em>报告称，根